'''重铬酸铯'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Cs<sub>2</sub>Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>。

==制备==
重铬酸铯可由[[重铬酸钠|重铬酸钠]]和[[氯化铯|氯化铯]]或[[硫酸铯|硫酸铯]]在70~80 °C混合，冷却后过滤沉淀，洗涤、重结晶得到。<ref>Shakhno, I. V.; Plyushchev, V. E. Synthesis of rubidium and cesium dichromate. ''Khimicheskaya Nauka i Promyshlennost'', 1959. 4: 685-686. ISSN: 0368-5586.</ref>它也可由[[碳酸铯|碳酸铯]]和[[三氧化铬|三氧化铬]]反应制得：<ref>Vinarov, I. V.; Fraiman, I. B.; Kolach, S. A. Complex preparation of reactive pure cesium salts from cesium chloride. ''Khimicheskaya Tekhnologiya (Kharkov)'', 1966. 6. 98-102. ISSN: 0368-699X.</ref>
: Cs<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> + 2 CrO<sub>3</sub> → Cs<sub>2</sub>Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> + CO<sub>2</sub>↑
==性质==
重铬酸铯可以和[[叠氮化钡|叠氮化钡]]反应，得到[[叠氮化铯|叠氮化铯]]。<ref>Csaszar, Lili M.; Rozsa, Karoly. Convenient method for producing small quantities of Cs metal. ''KFKI (Kozp. Fiz. Kut. Int.) Koezlemeny'', 1964. 12 (2): 175-179. CAN61: 82196.</ref>它和[[三氟化溴|三氟化溴]]反应，可以得到CsCrOF<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Chemical Society, Dalton Transactions|issue=11|language=en|issn=0300-9246|date=1984|pages=2445|doi=10.1039/dt9840002445|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=dt9840002445|title=Synthesis and properties of chromium(V) trifluoride oxide CrOF3 and related oxo-anions|accessdate=2020-12-11|author=Eric G. Hope, Peter J. Jones, William Levason, J. Steven Ogden, Mahmoud Tajik, Jeremy W. Turff}}</ref>它和[[五氧化二钒|五氧化二钒]]在430-550 °C反应，可以得到CsCrV<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>：<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=192|language=en|date=2012-08|pages=1–6|doi=10.1016/j.jssc.2012.03.025|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459612001909|title=Syntheses and properties of a series of chromium vanadates ACrV2O7 (A=Na, K, Rb, Cs) with layered structure|accessdate=2020-12-11|author=Yonggang Wang, Jie Liang, Ting Wen, Kuo Li, Yingxia Wang, Guobao Li, Fuhui Liao, Jianhua Lin|archive-date=2018-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703032018/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459612001909|dead-url=no}}</ref>
: 2 Cs<sub>2</sub>Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> + 4 V<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub> → 4 CsCrV<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> + 3 O<sub>2</sub>↑

它和[[草酸|草酸]]、[[草酸铯|草酸铯]]在溶液中混合，缓慢挥发溶剂可以结晶出暗蓝色的Cs<sub>3</sub>[Cr(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>]·2H<sub>2</sub>O。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section C Crystal Structure Communications|volume=66|issue=6|issn=0108-2701|date=2010-06-15|pages=m157–m159|doi=10.1107/S0108270110014861|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270110014861|title=Tricaesium tris(oxalato-κ 2 O 1 , O 2 )chromate(III) dihydrate|accessdate=2020-12-11|author=Lee Martin, Anthony Christian, Hiroki Akutsu|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220130251/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270110014861|dead-url=no}}</ref>

